## Documentation Updates Rule

### Documentation-only updates (no functional code changes):
- CHANGELOG.md
- PROJECT_OVERVIEW.md
- Code comments
- Inline documentation

### DO NOT increment CACHE_NAME version for:
- Grammar fixes
- Information updates
- Documentation restructuring
- Adding technical references
- Updating feature descriptions

### ONLY increment service worker version for:
- Game logic changes
- Bug fixes affecting gameplay
- New features implementation
- Asset updates (CSS, images, sounds)
- API changes
- Performance optimizations affecting player experience

